column5: Hummed and hawwed about heading out the other night after work and finally went for it.  We wouldn't normally keep so many but its been a long time since we brought home a meal.     the Pike came first after not even 5 minutes trolling and then before we finished the first pass we had a double header.    I think I may take another shot at them again tonight.
If I hop in the truck now, I can make it there in time for a midnight snack  Nice catch!!
Nice little fry yer gonna have !
Solid catch... Nice size walleye as well
Awesome stuff, Dara.  Nice fat fish....that will be a great fry-up for sure.
nice  and here I am drive by to go to a fly-in  better I don't catch too many that nice...........oh well we will see
The planets were aligned and the fish gods were with us that night. It all happened from 7 till 9 and then they shut down or moved on.
Looks like a good feed ya got there Dara and it always makes for a fun evening when the window opens on schedule.
Great haul.  Nothing beats a good walleye bite.
nice outing!  Got a trip to the Soo coming up in a couple weeks -(in-laws 50th)  be nice to get on to a few of those.
What were you using for bait? Dynamite?  Nice catch!!!
Nice catch! Again tonight eh? let me know how it pans out. headin out tomorrow for some pike n' eyes.  -JP
Great stuff Dara, haven't had a pickerel fry in awhile myself.  Enjoy
Nice bunch of walleye, they look fat!
Nice group of Walleye you got there! All of them look very healthy!
nicely done.  seems everybody has been doing real well the past week.  i'll have to try and get out one of these evenings.
some very nice eyes and a few pike to boot..!!!   cheers
